{"tid":981004,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国動物園皮包骨白虎餓到吃泥  園方指牠在吃地上食物殘渣","createTime":"2019-01-14T02:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T13:59:26.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"da00b24f38b7b5e622a66785dcf567386d832c13","tid":981004,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:29:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/01/11/4/5780753.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=350&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F01%2F11%2F4%2F5780753.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D350%26exp%3D3600&h=dc6ca72d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n楚天都市報報導，有網友表示，8日在大陸武漢動物園內發現一隻瘦削的白老虎，疑因太餓而舔食泥土。動物園其後回應稱，白老虎只是因趴下後腿骨凸起而顯瘦；又指牠當天早上已進食，事發時只是「意猶未盡」，舔食地上的食物殘渣。<br />\n<br />\n發現事件的王先生表示，當日下午4時許在武漢動物園遊玩期間，看見一隻白老虎走到室外，之後趴在沒有青草的地上，舔地上的泥土並咀嚼。王稱當時其視線範圍內「沒有看到任何類似於食物或是飼料之類的東西」。<br />\n<br />\n武漢動物園表示，這隻白老虎是去年從寧波引進，現年7歲，體重約120公斤，符合健康體重範圍，只是牠趴下時腿骨凸起才顯得瘦削，「站起來其實並不瘦」。園方指，牠當天早上近9時半將動物園提供的雞子叼到戶外進食，吃畢後「意猶未盡，舔食食物渣子像舔食泥土」。<br />\n<br />\n園方補充，園內每隻老虎每日有約5公斤食物，周二、周四餵食3隻雞子，周三、周五餵食牛肉，周日餵食脊骨；周一是禁食日，主要是調節改善胃腸功能，增進食欲，保持野性及控制體重。<br />\n<br />\n據武漢動物園老虎飼養員表示，平時沒有發現老虎吃土的現象；該院總工也介紹，貓科動物可能有誤食草的情況發生，不大可能吃土。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hHwEW9KGt3o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhHwEW9KGt3o&d=NpX4VTY7G2nO%2FOekE%2B%2FaMF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=c8d756ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hHwEW9KGt3o</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/7335/3587726\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F7335%2F3587726&d=NpX4VTY7G2nO%2FOekE%2B%2FaMF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=6a9dd2d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/7335/3587726</a>"},{"pid":"fff2f36e57451ef275571d68a5b7823cc54b4ba8","tid":981004,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"368ffae1f926546e265db2022dde74b208f4c939","tid":981004,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T02:37:22.000Z","msg":"死左就有白虎皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf1efeb59418bc2f908e4c27c68f88513915b9e","tid":981004,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e013be5c64ce4d876ec76cd43c051f6faef0b6e","tid":981004,"uid":115452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T13:59:26.000Z","msg":"動物唔係會食土嫁咩？<br />\n係想吸收mineral<br />\n<br />\n只少牛係"}]}